message: /* Speedy deletion nomination of Komala pata */
Robin Ch Roy (born 26th Jan 1984) is an Indian film writer, Actor, Director. He was born at Jhagrarpar, Dhubri in Assam.

Tor Bade Pran Kande (2008) is a Goalpariya superhit video film. It's written, produced & directed by Robin Ch Roy. Music by Sarajit sharma. The film casting is Nuruddin Mollah, Rupa, Ajibur Rahman, Bappi, Muktirani, Monsur and many more.
